Problem Name: Max Subarray Sum by Removing At Most One


---

1. Problem Statement

Given an integer array arr[], find the maximum sum of a non-empty contiguous subarray.

You are allowed to remove (skip) at most one element from the chosen subarray.

> Note: After removing one element, the remaining subarray must still be non-empty.



Return the maximum possible subarray sum.


---

