5. Brute Force Approach

Idea

Try deleting every possible element.

Also consider deleting nothing.

For each case,

run Kadane's Algorithm.

Take maximum answer.


---

Algorithm

For every index

Delete arr[i]

Run Kadane

Update answer

Also

Run Kadane without deletion


---

Code

class Solution:
    def maxSumSubarray(self, arr):
        n = len(arr)

        def kadane(nums):
            best = nums[0]
            curr = nums[0]

            for i in range(1, len(nums)):
                curr = max(nums[i], curr + nums[i])
                best = max(best, curr)

            return best

        ans = kadane(arr)

        for i in range(n):
            temp = arr[:i] + arr[i + 1:]

            if temp:
                ans = max(ans, kadane(temp))

        return ans


